{
  "stem": "23090.5",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was, to us, like a mitzvah, it was like the greatest thing that ever happened in the world to us.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Anyway, someone-- one of the guards saw us one night.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "One night we come in, and all the lights are on in the camp.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "This is about 7:00 at night.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the camp commander and all the Kappos are all out there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they have everybody out there, everybody, in the camp at an appell.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they take us up to these tables and they tell us to unload.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we unload all the-- this, this, this, these vegetables that we had brought there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And, again, this guy makes a speech that we entrusted these young Jews with an important this, and so on, and can't be trusted, and so on, so forth.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And this is the thanks, and we unloaded the stuff, and he's going to give us each 25 whips a piece, which was not out of the ordinary for the camp's punishment.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "There was like a table in the middle of the thing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And that's where they tied you down and they whipped you.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So there was one kid, kid's name was Schleimer, and he was a young-- he was very smaller kid, and so-- and we said, he isn't going to make it.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, we were-- and we're not trying-- I'm not trying to say here that we were trying to be heroes.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we asked the Kappo if one of us could take one or two of his, so that he-- you know, this kid could have never made it.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the camp commander said no, and we all got whipped 25 lashes for that.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he got whipped, and the kid died.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He died about a week later, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
